==Finnish==

===Demonstrative pronoun===
'''tämä''' (''stems'' '''tämä-''' ''and'' '''tä-''', ''see below'')

# [[this]].

====Declension====
The stem is '''tämä-''' in the genitive (accusative) only and '''tä-''' in other cases. The [[abessive]], [[comitative]] and [[instructive]] forms don't exist.

